My first rewrite; a reimagining of ObserverSeptember's controversial Martian Turtles.

This probably isn't what they originally intended, but it's still , as per their wishes. I've mainly cut redaction, while attempting to keep the air of mystery. I hope both fans and detractors of the original can enjoy this.

Many thanks to Captain Kirby.

